profile:
We love trees and would prefer keep a tree in all its glory as long as it is healthy.  However, sometimes a tree becomes damaged, distressed or diseased or has died. These trees can become dangerous as their weakened structures become vulnerable to weather conditions etc.  Sometimes, the tree needs to be trimmed back as it encroaches on high voltage wires or into our neighbors yards. An  unpredictable fall of tree or branches, can do a lot of damage to property and even persons. Don't wait until this happens to have this looked after.

TreeRock Inc. has been removing trees and shrubs safely for the last eight years. We come out to your property to assess the condition of the tree and make recommendations. We provide a free, detailed quote with no obligation to commit.
Our team is friendly and approachable and our clients are like family to us. Why don't you give us a call?  We'd love to meet you.


We're social here:
